{"id":149066,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/塔利班春季攻势开始/","date":"2011-05-01T15:00:21Z","modified":"2011-05-01T15:00:21Z","title":"塔利班春季攻势开始","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">喀布尔</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">联合国向阿富汗冲突各方发出呼吁，必须避免给平民百姓造成伤亡。联合国驻阿富汗高级代表米斯图拉</span><span>(Staffan de Mistura)</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">强调，不得有意攻击或杀害普通老百姓。在东南部省份帕克提亚</span><span>(Paktia)</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">发生的一次自杀袭击行动中，至少</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名平民丧生，</span><span>12</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人受伤。据悉，自杀袭击者是一名</span><span>12</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的少年。周六，极端组织塔利班宣布春季攻势开始并称，人群聚集的地方，军事基地，政府部门设施以及外国企业都是主要袭击目标。塔利班还告诫平民百姓远离这些目标。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15042548%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%A1%94%E5%88%A9%E7%8F%AD%E6%98%A5%E5%AD%A3%E6%94%BB%E5%8A%BF%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" t